{"tid":2445787,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"召喚歌唱求學巴絲及你問我答(六)","createTime":"2021-03-14T02:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T07:41:30.000Z","uid":77052,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"78acd0838721000fd2d7b8371802db246fb73c13","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係Hugo陳錦生<br />\n可能大家我嘅真名好陌生，不過如果我話我係子龍嘅話相信大家就知道我係邊個啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單介紹一下自己：我由十歲開始學唱歌，到十七歲開始教唱歌，一路至今已經過咗差唔多十五個年頭。<br />\n係呢段嘅時光入面，除咗教唱歌，自己都有去擔當一尐歌手同網路歌手嘅錄音指導(姐係係歌手錄音嘅時候指導佢哋果尐指導老師)、做過DEMO歌手、比賽評審等等<br />\n<br />\n係四年前2017年嘅1月18日，我係呢度出咗第一個post，同時亦開始咗我公開教學嘅生涯。<br />\n如果有了解我過往post嘅朋友，相信會知道呢幾年間我一直係臺大讀緊書，所以一直都分身乏術，無辦法去照顧同幫助到每一個身在香港嘅巴打絲打處理同解決係歌唱上嘅疑難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢一刻嘅我，覺得差唔多係時候了。<br />\n<br />\n無論係在自身歌唱系統理論上嘅完整度，抑或係自身目前可以付出嘅時間，以及係自身係歌唱嘅能力、甚至係自身歌唱能力以及教學於外人嘅肯定上等等，我都認爲呢一刻即便無辦法做到100分嘅完美，但起碼自問無愧於「見自己，見天地，見衆生」：<br />\n係理論嘅完整度上，我所獨創的系統基本上可以經受任何問題以及疑難的挑戰，而提出合理嘅回答以及解決問題嘅方案。<br />\n係時間方面，畢咗業嘅我選擇咗翻香港，從而全心全意投入呢一個終生嘅興趣當中。<br />\n自身嘅歌唱能力上，下列會有表演，比賽影片同唱K嘅時候手機錄嘅錄音比大家任意參考。<br />\n至於外人嘅肯定上呢一點，除咗學生嘅肯定外，自己係比賽上嘅表演，以及考獲Rockschool八級流行聲樂證書等，都係一種側面嘅證明。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TPtGi6urHz0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTPtGi6urHz0&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=912f7e7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TPtGi6urHz0</a><br />\n化名龍醇參加殘酷舞台嘅比賽片段(2020年9月)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sAXHV_ZIh44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsAXHV_ZIh44&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=a4a0da7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sAXHV_ZIh44</a><br />\n以下係幾首翻香港之前唱K時自己手機錄低嘅錄音(2021年1月，音質奇差+背景雜音多，多多見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n張惠妹 - 也許明天<br />\n<a href=\"https://voca.ro/1fJJcASoY4wc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvoca.ro%2F1fJJcASoY4wc&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=ddd6854d\" target=\"_blank\">https://voca.ro/1fJJcASoY4wc</a><br />\n蕭敬騰 - 皮囊<br />\n<a href=\"https://voca.ro/1necXpUIdVIX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvoca.ro%2F1necXpUIdVIX&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=81ce19e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://voca.ro/1necXpUIdVIX</a><br />\n林憶蓮 - 至少還有你<br />\n<a href=\"https://voca.ro/1cbBPoLFrL5O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvoca.ro%2F1cbBPoLFrL5O&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=786e5745\" target=\"_blank\">https://voca.ro/1cbBPoLFrL5O</a><br />\n陳奕迅 - 浮誇<br />\n<a href=\"https://voca.ro/1i0ZPVw494Qt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvoca.ro%2F1i0ZPVw494Qt&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=97cf6747\" target=\"_blank\">https://voca.ro/1i0ZPVw494Qt</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個post係代表我自己旅程真正嘅起點。<br />\n如果四年前嘅我係膽粗粗嚟見呢個世面嘅話，咁呢一刻嘅我就係做好萬全準備嚟迎接呢個瞬息萬變嘅世界。<br />\n所以係呢個post開始，除咗歡迎各位嚟吹水外、更歡迎各位嚟交流、求助等。<br />\n同時我都會開始係呢個post慢慢重新去update部分個人系統上嘅理念同諗法，比大家初步上對我嘅系統有個簡單嘅認識。<br />\n<br />\n目前我自己主要嘅服務有：Online/面對面歌唱教學(一對一/一對多)、Studio錄音/配唱指導<br />\n(多嘅唔多講，我雖然未必可以做到全港最平，但我堅信我嘅服務必然令你覺得物超所值)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>而最後係度送比大家嘅服務係：Telegram免費問事+免費聲音診斷<br />\n係呢十幾年入面，我研究咗各種唔同嘅歌唱教學系統，因此對坊間幾乎每種教學嘅系統都有一定嘅認識。因此我儘可能除咗樂意免費解答各位關於歌唱以及唔同流派上嘅困難外，更願意去免費去指出send片/錄音比我嘅巴絲打你哋聲音嘅問題係邊！<br />\n係呢個網上歌唱資訊千篇一律，求學動輒大大破費嘅時代中，免費嘅資源真係難得&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n作爲一個過來人，我比任何一個人都更明白呢樣嘢。<br />\n所以，我希望係我生存到嘅前提底下，為每一個重視自己聲音卻無充足資源拜師學習嘅有緣人盡一份綿力。<br />\n希望大家可以好好把握。<br />\nTelegram: @Hugo38983</ins></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWEM4Mo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWEM4Mo.jpg&h=c47826fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/euphrZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuphrZK.jpg&h=55712c74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef3adf051645a57b612e47e6f5208a99e789bd9c","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"追咗巴打之前嘅po 好有心教 <br />\n留個靚名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c538f8a49ce7fab253529431f85c6a3b8bebf88","tid":2445787,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"help push"},{"pid":"843fa09f55232b010ec3611a563241f2c53fd912","tid":2445787,"uid":31689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"我好中意唱歌 但唱得好難聽<br />\n<br />\n當年都有追你個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當日拜咗師 今日可能已經唔會五音不全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b19de26131b239c815270f62874c3968e53ea5","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3adf051645a57b612e47e6f5208a99e789bd9c","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"追咗巴打之前嘅po 好有心教 <br />\n留個靚名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有唔明嘅可以隨時問嫁~"},{"pid":"ce719262d01e2974e263da5930bf1819d095d2d6","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"843fa09f55232b010ec3611a563241f2c53fd912","tid":2445787,"uid":31689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"我好中意唱歌 但唱得好難聽<br />\n<br />\n當年都有追你個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當日拜咗師 今日可能已經唔會五音不全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"我相信有尐歌唱上嘅問題同缺陷係只有我先可以去處理<br />\n但，五音不全絕對唔屬於呢個範圍之內<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五音不全基本上就係音準嘅問題，咁音準嘅問題不外乎就係聽唔出/聽到唱唔出<br />\n咁當你分辨到個根本問題係邊度嘅時候，要去處理佢就絕對唔難嘅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15928d718577a87567b75e208a4cf3457c853b29","tid":2445787,"uid":72633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:24:30.000Z","msg":"比friend話我唱歌似講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全係平 冇音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪好難搞"},{"pid":"ebf5559e711db879a202ad7b3562798e55b4ea72","tid":2445787,"uid":201182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"跟utube d片學 其實係咪有用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68a2e74d117fd095de9065e9be2976cc1d7993f","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15928d718577a87567b75e208a4cf3457c853b29","tid":2445787,"uid":72633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:24:30.000Z","msg":"比friend話我唱歌似講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全係平 冇音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪好難搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"唱歌無起伏呢樣嘢，其實除咗情感嘅表達出問題外<br />\n亦有可能系本身發聲嘅問題導致嘅連貫性不足(呢一點亦有尐老師會以唔夠氣or唔夠連貫所表達)<br />\n所以重點係先要知道個問題係邊度<br />\n係歌唱上，我認爲只要有解決方案可以提供到出嚟，咁果樣嘢就唔會係一件難事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事在人爲，有無呢個恆心去透過長期嘅重複性練習而成功解決問題就真係要睇自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d1ef6d18199648e016df610af56877c6f1cfd7","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebf5559e711db879a202ad7b3562798e55b4ea72","tid":2445787,"uid":201182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"跟utube d片學 其實係咪有用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"見仁見智<br />\n不過，係我個人嘅角度睇落，係真係無用<br />\n首先，個老師所做嘅，所展示嘅嘢係唔係啱，呢個對一個無認知嘅人就已經係一個問號。<br />\n撇除呢一點唔講，最大個問題就係你跟住網路教學去學習之後，你所做出嚟嘅嘢，係無途徑比你知道你做嘅嘢係啱定係錯......<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(所以我嘅TG免費問事+聲音診斷就係為此而存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n不過其實最重要嘅，係首先要了解自己需要學尐乜<br />\n係呢個時代資訊咁發達嘅社會中，要搵學習嘅資源實在唔難<br />\n不過你自己如果唔知自己需要從邊方面下手提升自己嘅話，咁再多嘅教學都係徒然。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca31d0db5052a6e0ad1d3c01f586410ea2b1e6a3","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35b19de26131b239c815270f62874c3968e53ea5","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3adf051645a57b612e47e6f5208a99e789bd9c","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"追咗巴打之前嘅po 好有心教 <br />\n留個靚名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有唔明嘅可以隨時問嫁~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱沖涼隨口唱歌 醒起自己一上高音 一係好似合唱團咁吊高把聲 一係喉嚨太用力 好似嗌咁 把聲好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見啲歌手都係用真聲用力唱 但係聽落唔「銀」耳 仲覺得好有爆發性 渲染到情緒<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8089843925718b41a34d241879bdc5e5666225a5","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca31d0db5052a6e0ad1d3c01f586410ea2b1e6a3","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35b19de26131b239c815270f62874c3968e53ea5","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3adf051645a57b612e47e6f5208a99e789bd9c","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"追咗巴打之前嘅po 好